Uses of Class
org.jvault.metadata.API

  • Packages that use API 
    Package Description
    org.jvault.annotation
    Meta-information of Jvault about register beans, inject beans
    org.jvault.beans
    Package containing information related to Bean.
    org.jvault.extension
    A package that helps to extend Jvault API on Runtime.
    org.jvault.factory
    Package with JvaultFactory for creating Jvaults.
    org.jvault.factory.buildinfo
    Package that parameter of the JvaultFactory for build Vault and Bean.
    org.jvault.vault
    Packages containing Vault that manage generated Bean and inject it into user class.

    • Uses of API in org.jvault.annotation

      Classes in org.jvault.annotation with annotations of type API 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      interface  BeanWire
      Annotation that used in the class marked with VaultConfiguration
      This information is read from the AnnotationVaultFactoryBuildInfo class,
      and classes that will become InternalBean are found.
      interface  Inject
      Annotation to inject the corresponding InternalBean.
      interface  InternalBean
      Annotation that marks this class to be registered as a bean in Vault.
      interface  VaultConfiguration
      Annotation that used creating a VaultFactoryBuildInfo with class-configuration.

    • Uses of API in org.jvault.factory

      Classes in org.jvault.factory with annotations of type API 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  TypeVaultFactory
      Class that receives (String or VaultFactoryBuildInfo) and VaultType together,
      creates and returns a Vault implementation corresponding to the VaultType.
      interface  VaultFactory<T>
      Receives the VaultFactoryBuildInfo or String (the name of the Vault if the Vault already exists) value as an input, and returns the Vault.

    • Uses of API in org.jvault.factory.buildinfo

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractVaultFactoryBuildInfo
      Abstract class to help implement VaultFactoryBuildInfo interface.
      class  AnnotationVaultFactoryBuildInfo
      A class that reads the BeanWire marking information of the class marked with VaultConfiguration and returns the BuildInfo method.
      class  PropertiesVaultFactoryBuildInfo
      Receive the path of *.properties file and specify the return value of the VaultFactoryBuildInfo methods.
